ActionSA says it is patently evident that the ANC government has no plan to end our energy crisis. For more, eNCA speaks to ActionSA leader, Herman Mashaba. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Nersa is forcing South Africans to pick up the tab for corruption and mismanagement. ActionSA leader Herman Mashaba says that while the regulator considers Eskom's reasoning behind the latest tariff increase, it fails to consider Eskom's inability to hold its own accountable. READ: Nersa approves 18.65% tariff increase for Eskom He says Nersa is essentially handing the Eskom and government more money to be looted.